{"tid":2162791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果各位尊貴既立法會議員肯總辭，成立影子議會，我一定會捐十分一人工出來支持","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T11:40:44.000Z","uid":217430,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a82028f00d05e9ace691700a5fa8dcf0b950e9a9","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"老老實實，如果各位尊貴既立法會議員願意總辭，成立影子議會的話，我寧願日日捱麵包，都會捐十分一人工支持你們。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位議員想留係議會，無非都是這兩個原因。<br />\n<br />\n1）錢。<br />\n香港人窮得只剩下錢，各位肯成立影子議會的話，又何需擔心。幫鄺仔供斷層樓又點話呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）天真覺得可以抵擋惡法。<br />\n各位不是還覺得自己有能力阻止惡法通過吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">國安法<br />\n限聚令<br />\n緊急法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n看到這三個例子，無話可說吧。<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得留在立法會就是抗爭，sorry。對不起，你們只是自欺欺人，用抗爭名義吃人血饅頭。我寧願各位誠實一點，講明做議員只是為了「薪高糧準」。"},{"pid":"813ae5f7b68dc7ecb7ab66956b8cd9c6bf0a194d","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"早前五眼聯盟出聯合聲明，講到明mon撚住香港，要九月如期選舉。<br />\n<br />\n呢家中央委任多一年就狗衝。<br />\n<br />\n你估五眼見倒噤既畫面，會點諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f58f3c78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights</a>"},{"pid":"b3be1d5b6b7463e824ac058f8adf7e57a0898801","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e082d774918dd26ca0ac539e15a0adc549021c18","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9b42c23d911904118fbf2d3328d9ab9ca10f5a4","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a90080a624b33db19cfd4a8a7b71c73b931a2d4e","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d6126d18809a63daa0741555db99aabaea628b3","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b5d2da4f673a801ddaa347dd27111924f3c236d","tid":2162791,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fd1e9ac52cba40343b03218e4f47dadaa3ebe25","tid":2162791,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"push"}]}